title: Xmas '77 with The Sex Pistols - Sno
description:
Xmas '77 with The Sex Pistols

For the few guys 'n' gals that appreciate my uploads - here's your Xmas Bonus

Stick with it - this is slow to start but there's some quality previously unseen stuff here

Julien Temple has had footage of the Sex Pistols' final UK gig languishing in a rusty can for decades. Now it's being aired as part of this meditation on Christmas, which compares the festive seasons of 1977 and today via the medium of punk. 

Video 960 x 540 / 25 fps / 911 kbps / Xvid

Audio 128 kbps MP3

Duration 1:00

Seed to the Max and spread the love . . .

Merci beaucoup

Sno
